Floyd Mayweather and Manny Pacquiao will fight on May 2 in Las Vegas . 
  Kenny Bayless will referee the match and has overseen five of Mayweather's previous fights . 
  Oscar De La Hoya believes the appointment of Bayless gives Mayweather an advantage . 
  The 64-year-old has overseen Mayweather's pro debut against Roberto Apodaca in 1996 . 
 